- cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper discusses the integrated management of business processes and master data, which is a common concern in software engineering. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science): The paper proposes a formal model and discusses its potential in modeling, formal verification, and simulation, which are all topics related to logic in computer science. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages): The paper proposes a new formal model, which could be seen as a new programming language for modeling and simulation. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper discusses the foundations of the problem and proposes a new formal model, which could be seen as a contribution to the field of artificial intelligence in terms of knowledge representation and reasoning.
